N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 2103.7 - Failure to file

State Regulations

Where the landlord has failed to file a proper and timely
registration statement as required by this Part 2103, the Administrator may
establish the maximum rent pursuant to section
2102.6. Notes
